---
---
<section class="cta" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
  <div class="container cta-inner reveal">
    <h2 id="cta-heading">Seu manuscrito<br />merece ser <span class="cta-tone">publicado</span></h2>
    <p class="prose cta-sub">
      Fale com nossa equipe. Conte sobre o seu projeto e vamos encontrar o
      caminho certo para a sua publicação global.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/5581999999999?text=Olá!%20Vim%20pelo%20site%20e%20quero%20publicar%20meu%20livro."
        class="btn-white"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        Falar no WhatsApp
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#contato" class="link-white">Enviar mensagem</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    background: var(--amber);
    padding: clamp(89px, 13vw, 160px) 0;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 5.2vw, 4.2rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .cta-tone {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  }

  .cta-sub {
    margin: 0 auto var(--sp-4);
    max-width: 44ch;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* botão branco sobre âmbar */
  .btn-white {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 11px;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--amber);
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    padding: 17px 34px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: background var(--dur) var(--ease-out), transform var(--dur) var(--ease-out);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .btn-white:hover { background: var(--amber-mute); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-white svg {
    width: 17px; height: 17px;
    fill: none; stroke: currentColor; stroke-width: 2.2;
    stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* link branco sobre âmbar */
  .link-white {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 7px;
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    transition: color var(--dur), border-color var(--dur);
  }
  .link-white:hover { color: #fff; border-color: #fff; }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; gap: var(--sp-3); }
  }
</style>
